This is the BMW i Vision Circular, a supercar concept by BMW made of completely recyclable material with some of the coolest gadgets in the world.
Special thanks to @bmw for sponsoring this video. @bmwi

#futuremobility #bornelectric #circularity #urbanmobility #sustainablecar #rethink #ad
